Makeover

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/Hendrixer/ngFx into makeover

Conflicts:
	README.md
	src/animationsAssist.js
	src/transitionsAssist.js

feat(animations): add static animations

Static animations don't cause an enter/leave
Folders and files have been re-factored to reflect
You can can use these animations with $animate
Added two
  - .fx-tada
  - .fx-pulse

BREAKING CHANGE: you must now include the ngAnimate
module inside your app. ngFx no longer consumes it

Before:

angular.module('yourApp', ['ngFx'])

After:

angular.module('yourApp', ['ngFx', 'ngAnimate'])

This decouples all dependencies from ngFx and can
be entirely self managed
